<h2><strong>Features of web app (for officers):</strong></h2>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">View and accept or reject requests made by students</span></li>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Access points request page by clicking &ldquo;Point Request&rdquo; on Navbar</span></li>
