<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Access meetings page by clicking &ldquo;Meetings&rdquo; on Navbar</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br /><br /></span></li>
</ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">View who attended a meeting</span></li>
